transcripts.text: To my way of thinking, men have only one real problem.
Other men.  So how much of Colin's material did you steal, Louis?
A long time ago, men gave away their power to other men.

Giving something up to yourself, George, is called keeping it.  this rookie word-play of yours may impress and even invert the logical machinery of the jug-headed simpletons you usually talk to but to anyone with a piece of brain in their noggin all you're doing is haphazardly setting out the narrative.
